column5: I am assuming the hatch hasn't occrred yet, but don't recall anyone fishing Lac Seul to be concerned about them as some are in other lakes. i leave Friday and just wondering.
In my past 11 years of fishing LS you will probally enjoy the mayfly hatch next week. Usually hits the last 2 weeks of June. I'll be hittin it next week as well... Please leave a few fish for me....
